This product bundles, at build time, the prebuilt `aleo_rust` native library
built from the clean-room, Apache-2.0 `aleo_ffi` crate in this repository
(rust/aleo_ffi). That library statically links snarkVM (Apache-2.0) and its
transitive Rust dependencies. See THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.md for the third-party
attribution covering the statically-linked components.
